  <hr class="navbar__divider" />

  <main class="about">

    <h1 class="about__title">HOW IT WORKS</h1>

    <div class="cards">

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card__img">
          <img src="images/witch.png" alt="Ship arrives too late to save drowning witch" />
        </div>
        <p class="card__caption">SHIP ARRIVES TOO LATE TO SAVE DROWNING WITCH</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card__img">
          <img src="images/spider.png" alt="Spider doing a handstand on one leg" />
        </div>
        <p class="card__caption">SPIDER DOING A HANDSTAND ON ONE LEG</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card__img">
          <img src="images/camel.png" alt="Camel balancing books to improve posture" />
        </div>
        <p class="card__caption">CAMEL BALANCING BOOKS TO IMPROVE POSTURE</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <p class="about__description">
      These are droodles, a cartoon feature created by Roger Price. They are little drawings
      paired with a clever caption. It's time for you to make your own clever captions!
    </p>

    <a href="/game" class="randomize">RANDOMIZE</a>
